KARNAL BUNT - USA (TEXAS)
*************************
See Also
Karnal bunt - USA (California), Part 1 970714151412
Karnal bunt - USA (California), Part 2 970715174239
Karnal bunt - USA (California), Part 2: CORRECTION 970717172925
